headline: Prudential: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: NEWARK, N.J. (AP) — Prudential Financial Inc. PRU) on Tuesday reported fourth-quarter profit of $905 million. On a per-share basis, the Newark, New Jersey-based company said it had net income of $2.55.

headline: Prudential Financial, Inc. Announces Full Year and Fourth Quarter 2025 Results
summary: NEWARK, N.J., February 03, 2026--Prudential Financial, Inc. (NYSE: PRU) today reported full year and fourth quarter 2025 results.

headline: Prudential of Japan Implements Voluntary 90-Day Suspension of New Sales to Address Previously Disclosed Employee Misconduct
summary: TOKYO & NEWARK, N.J., February 03, 2026--The Prudential Life Insurance Company, Ltd. ("Prudential of Japan" or "POJ") and its parent company, Prudential Financial, Inc. ("PRU"), today announced a voluntary 90-day suspension of new sales activity at Prudential of Japan.
